Package: snowflakeoauth
Title: Connect to the 'Snowflake Data Platform' via 'OAuth' Clients
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
   person("Aaron", "Jacobs", , "aaron.jacobs@rstudio.com",
          role = c("aut", "cre")),
   person("RStudio", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
   )
Description: Snowflake database drivers support using 'OAuth' access
  tokens as a more secure and automated alternative to traditional
  password-based authentication. 'snowflakeoauth' implements the OAuth
  flows required to retrieve these tokens and facilitates opening 'DBI'
  connections to Snowflake with them.
